description:
Will Brinson, Pete Prisco and Jason La Canfora analyze the potential of a Johnny Manziel NFL comeback, evaluate Denver's recent draft history, breakdown the Colts actual hire this time of former Eagles OC Frank Reich, and discuss all coaching hires made this offseason.
